data.description: Welcome home to 501 W. Park Street in Hermitage! This beautiful ranch home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Enjoy an open concept with an eat-in kitchen and living room complete with high ceilings. Master bedroom includes a large ensuite master bathroom. A beautiful back deck gives way to a good sized back yard that features a fire pit and shed. A large attached 2-car garage has drywall and is heated. Home also has a peaceful front porch to enjoy on warm summer nights. Basement is open and ready to be finished. Furnace and hot water tank about nine years old. Property is in Hermitage school district. Don't miss out on your chance to see this home!
